pan></p><p style="margin:0pt; text-align:justify"><span style="font-family:Arial; font-size:11pt">&#xa0;</span></p><p style="margin:0pt 0pt 0pt 35.45pt; text-align:justify; text-indent:-35.45pt"><span style="font-family:Arial; font-size:11pt">1.3</span><span style="font-family:Arial; font-size:11pt">              </span><span style="font-family:Arial; font-size:11pt">The targets that ar</span><span style="font-family:Arial; font-size:11pt">e set relate directly to achieving the outcomes of the Police and Crime Plan and must be considered in tandem.  I shall therefore list the targets set under each priority.</span></p><p style="margin:0pt; text-align:justify"><span style="font-family:Arial; font-size:11pt">&#xa0;</span></p><p style="margin:0pt; text-align:justify; text-indent:35.45pt"><span style="font-family:Arial; font-size:11pt; text-decoration:underline">Priority 1:  Reduce the Number of Victims of Crime and Anti-Social Behaviour</span></p><p style="margin:0pt; text-align:justify"><span style="font-family:Arial; font-size:11pt">&#xa0;</span></p><p style="margin:0pt; text-align:justify"><span style="font-family:Arial; font-size:11pt">1.4</span><span style="font-family:Arial; font-size:11pt">              </span><span style="font-family:Arial; font-size:11pt">T</span><span style="font-family:Arial; font-size:11pt">argets set:</span><span style="color:#ff0000; font-family:Arial; font-size:11pt"> </span></p><p style="margin:0pt; text-align:justify"><span style="color:#ff0000; font-family:Arial; font-size:11pt">&#xa0;</span></p><ul type="disc" style="margin:0pt; padding-left:0pt"><li style="font-family:Symbol; font-size:11pt; margin:0pt 0pt 0pt 45.51pt; padding-left:18.29pt; text-align:justify; text-indent:0pt"><span style="font-family:Arial; font-size:11pt">Total crime – a decrease of 1% or more.</span></li></ul><p style="margin:0pt; text-align:justify"><span style="color:#ff0000; font-family:Arial; font-size:11pt">&#xa0;</span></p><ul type="disc" style="margin:0pt;